section.capitalization.description:
What is a LoWUpp?
The LoWUpp (Lowercase Uppercase) is the appearance of your nickname.
For example, Andre and AndRe are the same nickname, it's just the MajMiN that changes.

You can change MajMiN whenever you want.
You can only change the MajMiN of the letters, you cannot add any, you cannot remove any, you cannot exchange one letter for another.
section.capitalization.subtitle: A good LoWUpp is a plus for your recognition in the community...
section.eraser.description: Warning, you can only have one nickname at a time. If you already have a nickname and you buy one, the new one will replace the old one.
section.eraser.header: SOS moldy nickname, change your nickname for 200 credits!
wedding.description:
In our world, we can do lot of friends, it even sometimes happens that some go beyond friendship...

That's why our dear Guruji celebrates each wednesday, saturday and sunday beautiful weddings on the holy hill.
Only members that are single can do marriage proposal.
Those who want to break these sacred links should find the cave of Divorce and fight shame and fear.

The 3 couples that lasted the longest will earn married clothes.
